4. Andrew Solis

# Andrew Solis

## Visualization Laboratory Manager Visualization Interfaces & Applications

Phone: **512-475-9411** |
Email: **[asolis@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:asolis@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Andrew joined TACC as a full-time staff member in 2015, having previously worked for TACC as an undergraduate research assistant and vislab proctor. He is the laboratory manager for both the Visualization Lab (located in the Peter O'Donnell Jr. Building) and the Human Data Interaction Lab (located inside the J.J. Pickle Research Campus building). Andrew manages the labs and their students with the support of colleagues, and works on projects related to scientific visualization. His experience is in software development, having worked on projects related to virtual reality, web development, and visualization on HPC systems. Prior to working at TACC, Andrew worked for IBM.

### Current Projects

* Sculpting-Vis

### Areas of Research

* Scientific Data Visualization
* VR/AR/MR Systems and Application
* Web Development

### Education

**B.A., Computer Science,**  

University of Texas at Austin